            <p>Welcome to mind body and sole holistics. Based in Biggin, not far from Leeds and York I am a home-based therapist offering clinical reflexology, Reiki Healing and EFT (Emotional Freedom Technique). I have a diploma in clinical reflexology at VTCT Level 3 and I am a member of the Association of Reflexologists. I am a fully qualified Reiki Master and this is something I personally practise every day. I am also an EFT practitioner having completed levels 1 &amp; 2 and the full certification programme through EFT international of which I am also a member. I have always had a passion for holistic therapies as they consider the 'whole person' and integrate mind, body, spiritual and emotional forms of well-being in the quest for optimal health.</p>
